snippet.title: Inscribed Angles in Circles and Tangent Lines
snippet.description: I define Inscribed Angles, Inscribed Angles involving Tangent Lines, and 3 Corollaries of Inscribed Angles.  I work through five examples to help your understanding. Find free review test, useful notes and more at http://www.mathplane.com If you'd like to make a donation to support my efforts look for the "Tip the Teacher" button on my channel's homepage www.YouTube.com/Profrobbob
